<td style="padding-left:5px;">Delete within 3 months after promotion/competition ends</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="padding-left:5px;">Customer Care interactions</td>
<td style="padding-left:5px;">Open Account: Indefinite<br />
<br />
Closed Accounts:<br />
Duration of Licence + 2 years after termination in accordance with Clause 15.3 of Licence, but subject to Data Minimisation</td>
</tr>
